---
title: Double Greek-Style Beef Bowl with Veggie-Loaded Rice & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Beef and veggies can get a little tiresome, but we bet with this new twist, everyone at the table will be wanting a second helping. With flavours of garlic, a cooling yoghurt dolloped on top of an array of veggies and rice, it can be confirmed that beef and veggies are back in the good books!

